Xin Qian  03/09/2015
    toy MC to practice how to remove filter smearing function
    How to run "root -l abc.C"

gen_toy.C 
	  Generate toy MC results with field response
	  
gen_toy1.C 
	   Generate toy MC results without field response, just filter smearing 

invert.C 
	 Main code to remove the filter smearing function based on matrix operation
	 
plot_toy.C 
	Code to plot results from toy MC to see   

plot_filter.C
	Plot a filter function to see

plot_matrix.C
	Code to practice operate matrix in ROOT